Installation
------------
Here is how to build and install it on Debian GNU/Linux or Ubuntu Precise::

  sudo apt-get install help2man gettext automake bison build-essential flex libtool 
  sudo apt-get install liblog4cpp5-dev
  sudo apt-get install libglib2.0-dev libboost-all-dev liblo0-dev liblog4cpp5-dev
  sudo apt-get install gstreamer0.10-plugins-bad gstreamer0.10-plugins-base gstreamer0.10-plugins-good gstreamer0.10-plugins-ugly
  sudo apt-get install libavc1394-dev libdc1394-22-dev libdv4-dev libgstreamer-plugins-base0.10-dev libgstreamer0.10-dev 
  ./autogen.sh
  ./configure
  make
  sudo make install
  sudo ldconfig

